Can you arrange for them
to meet outside?

00:03:22.060 --> 00:03:23.660
Just once.

00:03:24.500 --> 00:03:25.340
Alright.

00:03:26.060 --> 00:03:26.900
I'll arrange

00:03:27.140 --> 00:03:27.980
for them to meet.

00:03:29.020 --> 00:03:30.420
Zhou Tingyan, you're really amazing.

00:03:31.340 --> 00:03:33.460
I'll go shopping with Tang
and buy some gifts.

