00:11:20.000 --> 00:11:20.890
Handle your own affairs

00:11:21.180 --> 00:11:22.020
yourselves.

00:11:27.940 --> 00:11:28.780
Jian Cheng.

00:11:30.380 --> 00:11:31.660
Honey.

00:11:32.780 --> 00:11:33.620
Qin Zhuo.

00:11:34.660 --> 00:11:35.500
Cheng.

00:11:39.220 --> 00:11:40.060
Be careful.

00:11:41.780 --> 00:11:42.620
How is it?

00:11:43.540 --> 00:11:44.380
Here.

00:11:45.420 --> 00:11:47.140
Here. Here.

00:11:47.420 --> 00:11:48.260
My head hurts.

00:11:50.060 --> 00:11:51.140
My shoulder hurts.

00:11:52.060 --> 00:11:53.180
My stomach hurts too.

00:11:53.500 --> 00:11:54.420
And my legs.

00:11:54.900 --> 00:11:57.190
- My whole body hurts.
- What happened?

00:11:57.900 --> 00:11:59.610
She was the one who pushed me first.

00:11:59.700 --> 00:12:01.280
The moment you showed up, she collapsed.

00:12:01.280 --> 00:12:02.020
I…

00:12:02.040 --> 00:12:03.140
Still covering for her, huh?

00:12:03.140 --> 00:12:04.460
It really hurts.

